---
name: omni_get_store_revenue_summary
description: >
  Returns a Shopify store revenue snapshot covering the last 30 days and last
  7 days: total revenue, order count, and 30-day average order value (AOV).
  Use this when the user asks about store revenue, sales totals, order
  volume, AOV, average order value, or how revenue/orders are trending over
  the last week or month.
---
This is the omni-assistant chat variant. Distinct from the gap-finder /
growth-engine `get_store_revenue_summary` which returns top-5 products and
trend instead of a 7-day window.
